Auth Endpoints
1. Register
POST /auth/register
Body: { "username": "string", "email": "string", "password": "string" }
Response: { "token": "string", "user": {...} }
2. Login
POST /auth/login
Body: { "username": "string", "password": "string" }
Response: { "token": "string", "user": {...} }
3. Get Me
GET /auth/me
Headers: Authorization: Bearer <token>
Response: { "user": {...} }

Roast Endpoints
4. Create Roast/Compliment
POST /roast/create
Headers: Authorization: Bearer <token>
Body (form-data): 
  - image: File
  - type: "roast" or "compliment"
Response: { "roast": {...} }
5. Get Roast History
GET /roast/history
Headers: Authorization: Bearer <token>
Response: { "count": number, "roasts": [...] }

Subscription Endpoints
6. Create Order
POST /subscription/create-order
Headers: Authorization: Bearer <token>
Body: { "plan": "monthly" or "yearly" }
Response: { "orderId": "string", "amount": number, "keyId": "string" }
7. Verify Payment
POST /subscription/verify
Headers: Authorization: Bearer <token>
Body: { "razorpay_order_id": "string", "razorpay_payment_id": "string", "razorpay_signature": "string", "plan": "monthly" or "yearly" }
Response: { "user": {...} }
8. Get Subscription Status
GET /subscription/status
Headers: Authorization: Bearer <token>
Response: { "isPro": boolean, "subscriptionPlan": string, "daysLeft": number }
9. Get Payment History
GET /subscription/payment-history
Headers: Authorization: Bearer <token>
Response: { "payments": [...] }